      "text": "動物は真に美しいものが分かるのですわ\n見なさい。この犬、私にすっかり懐いて甘噛みして……",
      "startTime": 247.1333401362,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_03-suz025.m4a",
      "text": "甘噛み……え、ちょっと噛む力が強過ぎ……いたたた！\n芽衣！　猫のお腹に顔を埋めてないで助けなさい！",
      "startTime": 259.3969505913,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
