      "text": "芽衣？　どうして私の頭をナデナデしてるんですの！？\n「可愛いな～」って、私は犬ではありませんわ～！",
      "startTime": 270.2999976475,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_08_03-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "（やれやれ……）\n（すずと芽衣が一緒にいると見ていて飽きないな）",
      "startTime": 277.2333350498,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
